definitions.definition: An unsophisticated resident of the towns of Oldham , Rochdale or surrounding areas. Now more widely applied to residents of any the satellite towns of Greater Manchester who speak with a broad Lancashire accent. A Lancashire hillbilly or bumpkin .

main_definition: ( UK , slang , derogatory ) An unsophisticated resident of the towns of Oldham , Rochdale or surrounding areas. Now more widely applied to residents of any the satellite towns of Greater Manchester who speak with a broad Lancashire accent. A Lancashire hillbilly or bumpkin .
